snippet.title: Fullstack MyJournal - iOS Get Post Delete Requests (Ep 4)
snippet.description:
With our HTML forms working, its time to move on and create an iOS application that can emulate the same functionality.  Namely, we'll want to fetch, create, and delete the post objects in our database by using Swift.

Previous Lesson: https://youtu.be/vVfremnOKXs
